{"tid":2395473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普拒絕於彈劾案中作證 轟民主黨譁眾取寵","createTime":"2021-02-05T02:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:36:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6875ea4f95c01c457d5d4eda57f6520a43192cd2","tid":2395473,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:21:28.000Z","msg":"2021/02/05 08:13<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美前總統川普卸任後還未公開露面，他的彈劾案審判將在下週展開，但他的律師已表明拒絕赴國會作證，痛斥民主黨的要求是「譁眾取寵的把戲」。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，眾院首席彈劾經理、民主黨籍眾議員拉斯金（Jamie Raskin）致信川普及其律師團，邀請他到國會為彈劾案作證，但遭律師團直接拒絕，「總統不會為不符合憲法程序的案件作證」，重申川普指控大選舞弊的言論受美國憲法第一修正案保護。<br />\n<br />\n川普律師團在回信中寫道，「你的來函只是確認了一個眾所皆知的事實：你們無法證明對已成為公民的第45任美國總統的指控屬實。」<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3432913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3432913&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=14060b75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3432913&h=a579cee2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3432913</a>"},{"pid":"ff5cce701ef458e34b1710791bfbaa39563d5104","tid":2395473,"uid":256837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"日日就喺度彈劾呢個彈劾嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有中國間諜醜聞嘅民主黨議員就睇唔到"},{"pid":"8674c3ec1b0ff6f6ecbbcf0b7d1377fff0ad101a","tid":2395473,"uid":82068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"你們無法證明對已成為公民的第45任美國總統的指控屬實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afca59b6f8d3d92cddef52c79c338e7a306e8a48","tid":2395473,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"共和黨幾時彈劾奧巴馬丶克林頓？<br />\n彈劾前總統喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}